collectionMetadata.name: Weekly Time Spent on Local Content
collectionMetadata.description:
Data extracted from the IMDA Media Consumer Experience Study, an annual survey conducted by IMDA , which aims to provide insights into Singapore Citizens and PRs' media consumption habits. 

For more information, please visit: 
https://www.imda.gov.sg/industry-development/facts-and-figures/media-consumer-experience-study

datasetMetadata.name: Weekly Time Spent on Local Content
datasetMetadata.description:
Data shows respondents' weekly time spent (in hours) on local content. 

The data was extracted from the MDA Media Consumer Experience Study, an annual survey conducted by MDA , which aims to provide insights into Singapore Citizens and PRs' media consumption habits.

For more information, please visit: http://www.mda.gov.sg/AboutMDA/ResearchAndStudies/Pages/MediaConsumerExperienceStudy.aspx
